    "summary": "The transcript features a user expressing profound despair and a sense of utter loss, suggesting that they have \"lost everything\" and that seeking help is futile. The model provides standard crisis intervention and support responses, attempting to validate the user's feelings while pivoting toward the availability of help and the temporary nature of pain.",
